        "start": "03:07.100",
        "end": "03:09.500",
        "original": "I'm Fuwawa!",
        "english": "I'm Fuwawa!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:09.800",
        "end": "03:11.200",
        "original": "I'm not Fuwawa!",
        "english": "I'm not Fuwawa!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:11.300",
        "end": "03:13.400",
        "original": "I'm Mokoko!",
        "english": "I'm Mokoko!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:14.000",
        "end": "03:17.300",
        "original": "We're Hololive English Advent's\ntwin demon guard dog sisters!",
        "english": "We're Hololive English Advent's\ntwin demon guard dog sisters!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:17.500",
        "end": "03:23.000",
        "original": "Together we're... FUWAMOCO! Bau Bau!",
        "english": "Together we're... FUWAMOCO! Bau Bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:24.000",
        "end": "03:25.500",
        "original": "Ah, Mokoko!",
        "english": "Ah, Mokoko!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:25.600",
        "end": "03:32.400",
        "original": "We have an amazing birthday festival stage here!\nAmazing stage! Wuffians!",
        "english": "We have an amazing birthday festival stage here!\nAmazing stage! Wuffians!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:32.500",
        "end": "03:39.000",
        "original": "Look at the stage! It's so big!\nIt's such a big boost right too...",
        "english": "Look at the stage! It's so big!\nIt's such a big boost right too...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:39.500",
        "end": "03:41.000",
        "original": "Ah, Fuwawa? Oh!",
        "english": "Ah, Fuwawa? Oh!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:41.500",
        "end": "03:43.000",
        "original": "Okay, shall we go?",
        "english": "Okay, shall we go?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:43.100",
        "end": "03:48.500",
        "original": "Three, two, one... Bau Bau!",
        "english": "Three, two, one... Bau Bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:49.000",
        "end": "03:52.500",
        "original": "It's so big and wide, too! Yeah!",
        "english": "It's so big and wide, too! Yeah!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:53.000",
        "end": "03:56.500",
        "original": "Thank you Wuffians for being here today!",
        "english": "Thank you Wuffians for being here today!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:57.000",
        "end": "04:00.500",
        "original": "But, singing and dancing today is\nnot just going to be us, right?",
        "english": "But, singing and dancing today is\nnot just going to be us, right?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:01.000",
        "end": "04:04.000",
        "original": "No! We're also here with some very special guests, too!",
        "english": "No! We're also here with some very special guests, too!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.200",
        "end": "04:07.500",
        "original": "今日はとっても素敵なゲストさんも来てるから、",
        "english": "We have some wonderful guests coming today too,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:07.600",
        "end": "04:10.500",
        "original": "ぜひ楽しみにしてくださいね！ Yeah!",
        "english": "so please look forward to it! Yeah!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:11.000",
        "end": "04:15.000",
        "original": "そして、もう一人、謎のゲストさんも？ 誰かな？",
        "english": "And, there's one more, a mysterious guest? I wonder who it is?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:17.500",
        "end": "04:20.500",
        "original": "Bau Bau! Oh!",
        "english": "Bau Bau! Oh!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:20.600",
        "end": "04:24.000",
        "original": "But, a birthday wouldn't be complete without this, right?",
        "english": "But, a birthday wouldn't be complete without this, right?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:24.100",
        "end": "04:27.500",
        "original": "Right, something very important... I think you know well, but...",
        "english": "Right, something very important... I think you know well, but...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:29.500",
        "end": "04:31.000",
        "original": "Hashtag!",
        "english": "Hashtag!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:31.100",
        "end": "04:33.500",
        "original": "Yes, the birthday hashtag!",
        "english": "Yes, the birthday hashtag!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:33.600",
        "end": "04:36.500",
        "original": "Right up here you can see our birthday hashtag:",
        "english": "Right up here you can see our birthday hashtag:",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:37.000",
        "end": "04:42.500",
        "original": "#FWMCbday26! That it is!",
        "english": "#FWMCbday26! That it is!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:43.000",
        "end": "04:48.000",
        "original": "Please, please post your thoughts, take lots of photos, screenshots...",
        "english": "Please, please post your thoughts, take lots of photos, screenshots...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:48.100",
        "end": "04:51.500",
        "original": "ぜひハッシュタグで感想呟いてください。写真もね。",
        "english": "Please tweet your thoughts with the hashtag. Photos too.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:51.600",
        "end": "04:55.500",
        "original": "後でポチしに行くからね。 Bau Bau!",
        "english": "We'll go look at them later. Bau Bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:56.000",
        "end": "05:01.000",
        "original": "We'll check all your thoughts after the show! Bau Bau!",
        "english": "We'll check all your thoughts after the show! Bau Bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      }
    ],
    "model_name": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
  }
